<item>
            <title>[LU-15740] runtests test_1: &apos;Space not all freed: now 8932kB, was 8788kB&apos;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15740</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Cliff White &amp;lt;cwhite@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/6363612b-d4a1-4780-9248-a54e1bf4bfea&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/6363612b-d4a1-4780-9248-a54e1bf4bfea&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_1 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&apos;Space not all freed: now 8932kB, was 8788kB&apos;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;May be a repeat of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10106&quot; title=&quot;runtests test_1: Space not all freed&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-10106&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-10106&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12807&quot; title=&quot;runtests test 1 fails with &amp;#39;&amp;#39;Space not all freed: now 180500kB, was 180424kB.&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-12807&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-12807&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12579&quot; title=&quot;runtests: test_1: @@@@@@ FAIL: Space not all freed: now 309264kB, was 307632kB.&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-12579&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-12579&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;VVVVVVV DO NOT REMOVE LINES BELOW, Added by Maloo for auto-association VVVVVVV&lt;br/&gt;
runtests test_1 - &apos;Space not all freed: now 8932kB, was 8788kB&apos;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
